<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Password Reset</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/CompleteGreet/FavIcon.png">

    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1 shrink">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/mdb.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Input-Style.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/Register.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="Box-Container">
    <div style="height: 560px;" class="row m-0">
        <div class="Join-OverView py-0 h-100 col-md-6">
            <div class="container ">
                <a href="/">
                    <img src="/images/CompleteGreet/Transparent-Side-Logo.png">
                </a>    <div>
                    <ul class="join-overview-list p-0">
                        <li class="mb-2">Officia voluptatibus incidunt qui et</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">Voluptas eveniet consectetur quis architecto.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2">Ab ipsum facere.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="join-overview-text mt-3 font-weight-normal">
                        Illo sint atque eos expedita. Exercitationem qui sunt qui ut doloremque a eos. Nulla laboriosam porro eos vero voluptas dolorem distinctio. Voluptatum inventore atque est non. Molestiae aperiam amet laboriosam est facilis repellendus architecto ea.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="Join-Form h-100 col-md-6 p-0">
            <div class="w-100 mb-4  mt-4">
                <h3 class="Register-Text ml-5">Password Reset.</h3>
                <span class="Register-SubText ml-5">Please enter your email</span>
            </div>
            <div class="join-form-container">
                <form action="/Password-Reset" id="Send-Email-Form" method="post" >
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-2"></div>
                        <div class="col-md-8 d-flex justify-content-center Reg-err">
                            <% include validations.ejs%>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-2"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">

                        <div class="col-md-12">
                            <label class="Input-Style auto-input-focus w-100">
                                <input name="email" id="Email" type="email" class="w-100" placeholder=" ">
                                <span>Email*</span>
                            </label>
                        </div>


                    </div>


                    <div class="col-md-12 mt-5 d-flex justify-content-center">
                        <button id="ForgetPass-Button" class="Login-Button">Send Email</button>
                    </div>

                </form>
            </div>

            <a href="/login" class="have-acc d-block text-center mb-2">
                Try another account?
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>


</div>
<script src="/js/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>

<script type="text/javascript" src="/js/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
<script type="application/javascript" src="/js/popper.min.js"></script>

<script type="application/javascript" src="/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script type="application/javascript" src="/js/mdb.min.js"></script>


<script type="application/javascript" src="/js/Login.js"></script>
</body>
</html>


